# Code Written

```python
from flask import Flask

# Create Flask Application
app = Flask(__name__)

# Home Page
@app.route("/")
def home():
    return "<h1>Welcome to AI Employee Salary Predictor</h1>"

# Run Flask Application
if __name__ == "__main__":
    app.run(debug=True)
```

---

# Code Explanation

| Code | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `from flask import Flask` | Import Flask Framework |
| `app = Flask(__name__)` | Create Flask Application |
| `@app.route("/")` | Create Home Page Route |
| `def home():` | Home Page Function |
| `return "<h1>...</h1>"` | Send HTML Response |
| `app.run(debug=True)` | Start Flask Development Server |

